{"tid":1851323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 香港人，仲唔反佢老母","createTime":"2020-01-30T03:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T10:59:11.000Z","uid":258731,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d247422a79888b2104178122ecb43452c47756b1","tid":1851323,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9438bc3a8829369ed13234fe4adac97a30f053e","tid":1851323,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"（港人自救教學）如何逼使中共容許支那人落嚟香港？<br />\n答案：香港作為革命起源地，當然要輸出革命，教曉佢哋點樣作反，要將香港式「時代革命」傳染返中國！<br />\n<br />\n1) 方法一：流動式文宣（口罩／T-Shirt等）<br />\n<br />\n**首選：請於口罩上寫上／貼上 「福建獨立」 ，「廣州建國」，「武漢起義」，「上海獨立」，「推翻中共」，「打倒共產黨」等字句<br />\n<br />\n次選：「光復香港」，「香港獨立」，「青天白日滿地紅」，「小熊維尼」等當然都可以<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stjuvEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstjuvEM.jpg&h=29272a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）方法二：公眾地方鳩叫<br />\n<br />\n3）方法三：Airdrop文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/1CiVarU.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/ijbzq0e.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n4）方法四：連儂牆<br />\n唔多講了，之前做開嘅嘢而家更加要加大力度做<br />\n唔好在局限係特定連儂牆<br />\n黨鐵站，巴士站，廁所，商場都可以係連儂牆<br />\n快快手貼，貼完就走<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/lab/extradition_gallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Flab%2Fextradition_gallery&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=e5ddbfa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/lab/extradition_gallery</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/83929522_180675446634158_1050267439725543424_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ohc=NpMpg_l56mgAX84nSRY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=421ff20c2383d8d319dcc82aef668ea4&amp;oe=5ED85DE6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F83929522_180675446634158_1050267439725543424_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ohc%3DNpMpg_l56mgAX84nSRY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D421ff20c2383d8d319dcc82aef668ea4%26oe%3D5ED85DE6&h=3a7d1699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔"},{"pid":"5609b1e46a5d8425d6c3f1119621efc4ec330645","tid":1851323,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=072d4e50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"f3ae2da259d3ce46b20645fca76884e28c159cd4","tid":1851323,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d247422a79888b2104178122ecb43452c47756b1","tid":1851323,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\